					<description><![CDATA[MTN’s IHS Towers acquisition could reshape connectivity, competition, and startup opportunities across Francophone Africa’s digital economy.]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
